        "message": "Patch Set 5:\n\nhello, Marcus,\n          for the CreateVcpeResCustService.groovy file, there are so many change about the space/tab etc. which makes the code hard to review. \n          is it possible to avoid this like only submit the code change? :)",
        "patchset_number": 5
